{"tid":1453457,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國旗及國徽法係唔包括共產黨旗","createTime":"2019-08-12T04:15:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T04:42:39.000Z","uid":32722,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d29a8d1c528e4a5caf71a57c019cd6d6bcbe5b27","tid":1453457,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:15:06.000Z","msg":"大家都知我一向愛國愛港, 都冇諗過香港要獨立<br />\n我最睇唔過眼既係某國既執政黨成日係度說三道四<br />\n所以燒國旗同扔國旗落水唔係我杯茶<br />\n反而某黨既黨旗我就反而有點興趣<br />\n橫掂又唔犯法, 689 想懸紅, 捉到人都告唔入<br />\n點解大家唔一齊企出黎向執政黨說不? <br />\n重點係冇人扣到港獨帽子架"},{"pid":"7d117e099c8460275fb0495a3773753c627b577b","tid":1453457,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:18:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以燒國旗同扔國旗落水唔係我杯茶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收工啦你"},{"pid":"da64c00fddb5b4af85de923da0a1791e34e0076b","tid":1453457,"uid":81894,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7d117e099c8460275fb0495a3773753c627b577b","tid":1453457,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:18:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以燒國旗同扔國旗落水唔係我杯茶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收工啦你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11f25e98e85abe94d2f96fa55d2af9ab1fa1c07","tid":1453457,"uid":97371,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:21:41.000Z","msg":"畫花幅黨旗就得, 然後示眾<br />\n<br />\n唔好放火燒俾人告縱火。"},{"pid":"dd97248e51bf82aeb697e70a0cc387c18046b091","tid":1453457,"uid":54921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:22:39.000Z","msg":"其實中共唔係共產黨而係納粹黨<br />\n一個民族 一個國家 一個元首"},{"pid":"20fe912006b41df9eb8bd1434d0f81346c259567","tid":1453457,"uid":32722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:23:38.000Z","msg":"文件 A401 《國旗及國徽條例》<br />\n<br />\n1.簡稱<br />\n(1)本條例可引稱為《國旗及國徽條例》。<br />\n(2)(已失時效而略去&mdash;&mdash;2017年第1號編輯修訂紀錄)<br />\n2.釋義<br />\n(1)在本條例中，除文意另有所指外 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n規格 (specifications)指分別列於附表1及2的國旗或國徽規格；<br />\n國旗 (national flag)指1949年9月27日中國人民政治協商會議第一屆全體會議決議通過的中華人民共和國國旗；<br />\n國徽 (national emblem)指1950年6月28日中央人民政府委員會第八次會議通過的中華人民共和國國徽。<br />\n(2)國旗的規格列於附表1。<br />\n(3)國徽的規格列於附表2。<br />\n<br />\n冇提及過共產黨旗"},{"pid":"9df81431a0a8de8c0d6e39fa5a5ad298195733e9","tid":1453457,"uid":127922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:23:42.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"bf03c5169628b3749b00a34c34665207a1b81144","tid":1453457,"uid":60006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:24:43.000Z","msg":"燒警徽"},{"pid":"1dfb525c792062d8051cd5cd57339d30490f09ca","tid":1453457,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d117e099c8460275fb0495a3773753c627b577b","tid":1453457,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:18:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以燒國旗同扔國旗落水唔係我杯茶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收工啦你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:42:39.000Z","msg":"佢曲"}]}